{"tid":1374290,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"根本港共／後面啲人唔識得濫用抗生素嘅後遺症","createTime":"2019-07-27T17:56:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T03:31:06.000Z","uid":11598,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f580524460837b80fbb271415dbca8f16427b1c4","tid":1374290,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:56:05.000Z","msg":"有用過抗生素嘅都知道 一定唔可以亂用<br />\n因為濫用抗生素會導致啲細菌產生抗藥性<br />\n最後抗生素就會對呢隻菌無效用<br />\n<br />\n啲智囊真係豬閪嚟 前線嗰啲更加連豬閪腦都無 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前催淚彈都逐粒逐粒放<br />\n612 第一次連續放幾粒<br />\n而家一放催淚彈好似落雨咁撚樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n清完 埋位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每個星期我見到嘅係幫緊我哋刷經驗<br />\n不論勇武定企後面撐人數嘅<br />\n大家已經有晒技能 熟晒手<br />\n工程手足拆鐵馬鐵欄快過打針 隔離和理非自動落雨開遮<br />\n綁三角鐵馬已經變咗基本嘢<br />\n由本來好鍾意死守 整晒路障實一實<br />\n變到而家唔再留戀鐵馬陣 來去如風<br />\n個心態同環境已經完全變晒<br />\n<br />\n如果有一日可以跨越到玩火呢個政治潔癖里程碑<br />\n我相信 雞尾酒療法將會成為主流<br />\n但係出到雞尾酒 亦都即係話我哋已經迫到冇得返轉頭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf164333d90d00d026bcdf52064989ef51cfcc58","tid":1374290,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:57:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b31b0e83a51d3e954a228268678994b355c26923","tid":1374290,"uid":6556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:58:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edc6c1e0ca65befd5610a506ebc516c86541fefd","tid":1374290,"uid":277186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:59:16.000Z","msg":"諗住打佢d示威者驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地無人驚 而且唔會驚"},{"pid":"7134f90a790db5f262820329356dccddb551c1ff","tid":1374290,"uid":3513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"